4717struct ucd_decomposition_info {
4718 constexpr static unsigned cp_index_width = 15;
4719 constexpr static unsigned cp_size_width = 5;
4720 constexpr static unsigned type_width = 5;
4721
4722 using value_type = uint32_t;
4723 static_assert(cp_index_width + cp_size_width + type_width <= sizeof(value_type) * CHAR_BIT);
4724
4725 value_type value;
4726
4729 [[nodiscard]] constexpr size_t cp_index() const noexcept
4730 {
4731 return value >> (cp_size_width + type_width);
4732 }
4733
4736 [[nodiscard]] constexpr size_t cp_size() const noexcept
4737 {
4738 constexpr auto mask = (value_type{1} << cp_size_width) - 1;
4739 return (value >> type_width) & mask;
4740 }
4741
4744 [[nodiscard]] constexpr unicode_decomposition_type type() const noexcept
4745 {
4746 constexpr auto mask = (value_type{1} << type_width) - 1;
4747 return static_cast<unicode_decomposition_type>(value & mask);
4748 }
4749
4755 [[nodiscard]] constexpr bool should_decompose(size_t decomposition_mask) const noexcept
4756 {
4757 return to_bool((1_uz << to_underlying(type())) & decomposition_mask) and cp_size() != 0;
4758 }
4759
4766 [[nodiscard]] constexpr std::u32string decompose() const noexcept
4767 {
4768 auto r = std::u32string{};
4769 hilet first = cp_index() * detail::ucd_decompositions_code_point_width;
4770 hilet last = first + cp_size() * detail::ucd_decompositions_code_point_width;
4771
4772 for (auto i = first; i != last; i += detail::ucd_decompositions_code_point_width) {
4773 r += wide_cast<char32_t>(load_bits_be<detail::ucd_decompositions_code_point_width>(
4774 detail::ucd_decomposition_code_points_bytes, i));
4775 }
4776 return r;
4777 }
4778
4785 [[nodiscard]] constexpr std::optional<char32_t> canonical_equivalent() const noexcept
4786 {
4787 if (type() == unicode_decomposition_type::canonical and cp_size() == 1) {
4788 hilet offset = cp_index() * detail::ucd_decompositions_code_point_width;
4789 return char_cast<char32_t>(load_bits_be<detail::ucd_decompositions_code_point_width>(detail::ucd_decomposition_code_points_bytes, offset));
4790 } else {
4791 return std::nullopt;
4792 }
4793 }
4794};
4795
4798[[nodiscard]] constexpr ucd_decomposition_info ucd_get_decomposition(char32_t code_point) noexcept
4799{
4800 constexpr auto max_code_point_hi = detail::ucd_decompositions_indices_size - 1;
4801
4802 auto code_point_hi = code_point / detail::ucd_decompositions_chunk_size;
4803 hilet code_point_lo = code_point % detail::ucd_decompositions_chunk_size;
4804
4805 if (code_point_hi > max_code_point_hi) {
4806 code_point_hi = max_code_point_hi;
4807 }
4808
4809 // The index in the chunk-index table based on the upper-bits of the code-point.
4810 hilet chunk_index = load_bits_be<detail::ucd_decompositions_index_width>(
4811 detail::ucd_decompositions_indices_bytes,
4812 code_point_hi * detail::ucd_decompositions_index_width);
4813
4814 // Add back in the lower-bits of the code-point.
4815 hilet index = (chunk_index * detail::ucd_decompositions_chunk_size) + code_point_lo;
4816
4817 // Get the decomposition value from the decomposition table by index.
4818 hilet value = load_bits_be<detail::ucd_decomposition_width>(
4819 detail::ucd_decompositions_bytes, index * detail::ucd_decomposition_width);
4820
4821 return ucd_decomposition_info{narrow_cast<ucd_decomposition_info::value_type>(value)};
4822}
